<br>
<h2>1. Ticket Cancellations and Refunds</h2>
Ticket Cancellation: Tickets once booked through the website or mobile app cannot be canceled. However, under exceptional circumstances, a refund may be requested, subject to approval.<br>
<br>
Refund Eligibility: Refunds may only be issued in cases of:<br>
<br>
Cinemas Closing: If a movie is canceled or rescheduled and you are unable to attend, you are eligible for a full refund.<br>
Technical Issues: If the cinema system malfunctions, resulting in an inability to watch the film, a refund may be processed.<br>
Non-Refundable Tickets: Tickets purchased for special events, premieres, or shows marked as "non-refundable" cannot be refunded once purchased.<br>
<br>
<h2>2. Refund Processing</h2>
Method of Refund: All refunds will be processed to the original payment method used during booking.<br>
